  "instruction": "Do strings ka longest common substring nikalne ke liye aik function likhiye.",
  "input": "",
  "output": "def longest_common_substring(s1, s2):
    # String ki lambai initialize karein.
    m = len(s1)
    n = len(s2)
  
    # Longest common substring initialize karein
    result = ""
  
    # Dono strings ki lambai se shuru karein
    # aur do indices set karein
    for i in range(m): 
        for j in range(n): 
  
            # Counter initialize karein
            count = 0
  
            # Longest common substring dhoondein
            while (i + count < m and 
                   j + count < n and 
                   s1[i + count] == s2[j + count]): 
                count+= 1
  
            # Longest common substring update karein
            if count > len(result): 
                result = s1[i:i + count] 
    return result"
}

Yeh paanch afraad par mushtamil tha: maa, baap, aur teen chhote bachay. Woh aik dosray ka khayal rakhte thay, aur un ke din zameen par dana chugne aur qareebi darakhton mein ghonsle banane mein guzar jatay thay. Woh mil kar meethi aawaz mein gaate, jis se waadi mehalon se bhar jati thi.

Jab sardi aayi, to khandan ne aik dosray ke saath mil kar kaam kiya taake un ka chhota jhund thandi mosam mein zinda reh sake. Maa chhote keere aur anaj ke tukde dhoondhne mein behtareen thi, jo bachon ki nashonuma ke liye zaroori ghiza faraham karti thi.

Thrushes un chand janwaron mein se thay jo waadi mein lambi, sardi raaton mein zinda rahe. Bahar ke aane aur mosam garam hone par, khandan taraqqi karta gaya. Chhote bachay bare parinday ban gaye, jo zindagi aur khushi se bhar gaye thay aane wali garmi ke liye. Thrushes ki aawaz lagbhag har din sunayi deti thi, chahe koi bhi mosam ho.
